title: Somewhat Favorable Press Coverage Somewhat Unlikely to Affect RealNetworks (RNWK) Share Price
content: Press coverage about RealNetworks (NASDAQ:RNWK) has trended somewhat positive recently, Accern Sentiment reports. The research firm rates the sentiment of news coverage by monitoring more than twenty million news and blog sources in real-time. Accern ranks coverage of companies on a scale of negative one to one, with scores closest to one being the most […]
